Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/tdickman/dotvim.git ~/.vim

OSX:

    brew install vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Install dependencies:

    vim +PlugInstall +qall

Source: http://dudarev.com/blog/keep-vim-settings-and-plugins-in-git-repo/
